description: Headlines provides you with the top stories from the New York Times from a variety of sections. Simply ask for the top stories in the section you're interested in. The data is provided by The New York Times, but The New York Times is not affiliated with this skill.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask top headlines for the top stories
Alexa, ask top headlines what the top stories in technology are
Alexa, ask top headlines for the top stories in business
name: Top Headlines
shortDescription: Listen to the top story headlines from The New York Times.
